Source: plpgsql-check
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/okbob/plpgsql_check

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-plpgsql-check
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-plpgsql-check
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: PL/pgSQL function validation and profiling tools for PostgreSQL
  plpgsql_check provides direct and indirect validation, profiling, tracing,
  and dependency inspection tools for PL/pgSQL functions.
